Resources for Angular Developers

Introduction to Observables (from Rxjs library) for Angular Developers
https://developer.telerik.com/topics/web-development/introduction-observables-angular-developers/

Rx Marbles: Interactive Design for visualizing how operators (like functions with Observable streams for input/output) work on one or more streams to produce an output stream(s)
http://rxmarbles.com/






